data.description: This stunning home will have you amazed as you walk thru. Built in 2021, this home offers 4290 sq.ft., 5 br, 3.5 ba, foyer, formal dining room with a coffered ceiling, lg grand room with a gas fireplace, beautiful gourmet kitchen with a large island designed for bar stools, lots of cabinets, wall oven & microwave, gas stove top with lg drawers below & a pull out spice rack on each side of the drawers, pot filler, beautiful back splash & quartz countertops, huge breakfast area, lg laundry rm with cabinets & sink, half bath, lg master bedroom with a sitting room, master bath with soaking tub & sep. lg tiled shower, water closet & double vanities, lg master closet, beautiful rod iron on the staircase. Upstairs are 4 huge bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms & lots of storage, there is a covered screened enclosed back patio & privacy fenced backyard, side entry 2 car garage. Extras & upgrades consist of: termite bond, house plans, security system, spray foam insulation, HVAC system with built in humidifier, beautiful hardwood flooring thru-out the first floor with tile in the laundry & bathrooms, upstairs offers carpet in all bedrooms, hardwood in the large hall area & tile in the bathrooms, quartz countertops thru-out the home, 7" baseboard, rain showerhead in the master suite shower, tankless hot water heater & last but not least, gutters. This home is in Charleston Mills Subdivision, has a beautiful community pool, transferrable 2-10 warranty, priced to sell! Don't miss this beauty
